<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Confirmação de E-mail - CardMaster</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Confirme seu e-mail para ativar sua conta no CardMaster.">
    <meta name="keywords" content="cardmaster, e-mail, confirmação, ativar conta">
    <meta name="author" content="CardMaster">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap');
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 flex flex-col min-h-screen">
    <header class="bg-white shadow-md py-4">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <nav class="flex justify-between items-center">
                <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">CardMaster</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="flex-grow flex items-center justify-center py-12 px-4">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-xl p-8 max-w-md w-full text-center">
            <i class="fas fa-envelope-open-text text-6xl text-blue-600 mb-6"></i>
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-4">Confirme seu E-mail</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Enviamos um link de confirmação para o seu e-mail. Por favor, verifique sua caixa de entrada e clique no link para ativar sua conta.</p>
            <div class="mb-6">
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Não recebeu o e-mail?</p>
                <button class="mt-2 text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-semibold">Reenviar e-mail de confirmação</button>
            </div>
            <a href="/" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline inline-block transition duration-300">
                Voltar para a Página Inicial
            </a>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-white py-6 mt-auto">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-sm mb-2">&copy; 2024 CardMaster. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
            <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4">
                <a href="/termos-de-uso" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition duration-300">Termos de Uso</a>
                <a href="/politica-de-privacidade" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition duration-300">Política de Privacidade</a>
                <a href="/suporte" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition duration-300">Suporte</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
